'''[[祆教|祆教]]'''是[[巴哈伊信仰|巴哈伊信仰]]承认的曾在宗教经典中预言[[巴哈欧拉|巴哈欧拉]]出现的九大宗教之一。[[琐罗亚斯德|琐罗亚斯德]]被认为是连续出现的[[上帝的显示者|上帝的显示者]]之一。[[祆教|祆教]]宗教经典《[[阿維斯陀|阿維斯陀]]》的真实性被认为是不确定的。<ref name="smith-zoroastrianism">{{cite encyclopedia |last= Smith |first= Peter |encyclopedia= A concise encyclopedia of the Baháʼí Faith |title= Zoroastrianism |year= 2000 |publisher= Oneworld Publications |location= Oxford |isbn= 1-85168-184-1 |pages= 369 |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=pYfrAQAAQBAJ |access-date= 2020-08-16 |archive-date= 2019-04-01 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190401083644/https://books.google.com/books?id=pYfrAQAAQBAJ |dead-url= no }}</ref>

==巴哈欧拉的血统==
巴哈欧拉，原名为米尔扎·侯赛因·阿里，是琐罗亚斯德及[[萨珊王朝|萨珊王朝]]最后一位君主[[伊嗣俟三世|伊嗣俟三世]]的后裔。<ref name="smith-zoroastrianism" />他的父亲是[[波斯|波斯]][[馬贊德蘭省|馬贊德蘭省]]的贵族。米爾紮·阿布-法則勒写过关于巴哈欧拉血统的论文。<ref>{{Cite book |last = Balyuzi |first = H.M. |authorlink = Hasan M. Balyuzi |year = 1985 |title = Eminent Baháʼís in the time of Baháʼu'lláh |publisher = George Ronald |location = Oxford, UK |isbn = 0-85398-152-3 |pages = 309–312 |url = http://sites.google.com/site/akbweb/Ancestry_of_Bahaullah.pdf |access-date = 2020-08-16 |archive-date = 2020-04-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200416143923/https://096b00bd-a-62cb3a1a-s-sites.googlegroups.com/site/akbweb/Ancestry_of_Bahaullah.pdf?attachauth=ANoY7cr7LE3Vshpnptu8YuQqUkr3t2GnJVyT5J3BcIejIARzAVaoir1_1GLNLh3WAGoGGjdPz-NW-cZlJJJvLm59NaRVG10g1cDHtBxnPFvajXHc1A-Dbg1wcwxhqtOw2ZgD8IJ1Lap6vQEzrVL2pA6eq_sqilBtu0j8nfJEzfkNXPOvY6nUg8rFkBhfgMsGuPY_AX00qYdC9fKQYZ-RSMJ9JZI7SJvaNA==&attredirects=0 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |last = Balyuzi |first = H.M. |authorlink = Hasan M. Balyuzi |year = 2000 |title = Baháʼu'lláh, King of Glory |publisher = George Ronald |location = Oxford, UK |pages = 9–11 |isbn = 0-85398-328-3 }}</ref>

==预言==
祆教预言了拯救世界的苏什扬特或夏巴兰的到来。巴哈伊认为巴哈欧拉的到来实现了上述预言。<ref name="smith-zoroastrianism" /><ref>{{Cite book |last = Kazemi |first = Farshid |year = 2013 |title = Irfan Colloquia |volume = 14 |contribution = Celestial Fire: Baháʼu'lláh as the Messianic Theophany of the Divine Fire in Zoroastrianism |publisher = Irfan Colloquia |location = Wilmette, IL |isbn = 978-3942426183 |pages = 45–123 |chapterurl = http://bahai-library.com/kazemi_celestial_fire |ref = harv |access-date = 2020-08-16 |archive-date = 2020-03-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200323163100/http://bahai-library.com/kazemi_celestial_fire |dead-url = no }}</ref>

==文献来源==

《[[大同圣帐|大同圣帐]]》是巴哈欧拉所作的书信集，其中包括对知名的祆教徒Mánikchí Limjí Hataria以波斯语写成回复，和对其秘书Mírzá Abu'l-Faḍl写的说明。上述作品和其他三份书简简单体现了巴哈欧拉和祆教的关系。

==早期的改宗情况==
在19世纪，祆教社区大量集中在波斯的[[亚兹德|亚兹德]]与[[克尔曼|克尔曼]]地区。而在印度，祆教徒则以[[帕西人|帕西人]]为人所知，他们大量集中在[[孟买|孟买]]。<ref name="maneck-1984">{{cite book| last =Maneck| first =Susan Stiles| editor-last =Cole| editor-first =Juan R. I.| editor2-last =Momen| editor2-first =Moojan| title =Iran East and West: Studies in Babi and Baha'i History| chapter =Early Zoroastrian conversions to the Baháʼí Faith in Yazd, Iran| chapterurl =https://books.google.com/books?id=7xbzoJ5wFG4C&lpg=PP1&pg=PA67| publisher =Kalimat Press| series =Studies in Babi and Baha'i History: From Iran East and West| volume =2| edition =illustrated| year =1984| pages =67–93| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=7xbzoJ5wFG4C| isbn =9780933770409| access-date =2020-08-16| archive-date =2016-04-25| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160425045018/https://books.google.com/books?id=7xbzoJ5wFG4C| dead-url =no}}</ref>自1880年代以来，大量亚兹德的祆教徒改宗巴哈伊信仰，而类似的情形亦发生在孟买并成为当时孟买巴哈伊社区成长的一大因素。<ref name="smith-zoroastrianism" />第一个祆教改宗巴哈伊信仰的信徒据信是亚兹德的Kay-Khusraw-i-Khudádád。<ref>{{Cite book |last = Taherzadeh |first = A. |author-link = Adib Taherzadeh |year = 1984 |title = The Revelation of Baháʼu'lláh, Volume 3: ʻAkka, The Early Years 1868-77 |publisher = George Ronald |place = Oxford, UK |pages = 269 |isbn = 0-85398-144-2 |url = http://www.peyman.info/cl/Baha'i/Others/ROB/V3/p253-274Ch12.html |access-date = 2020-08-16 |archive-date = 2018-08-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180826150704/http://www.peyman.info/cl/Baha'i/Others/ROB/V3/p253-274Ch12.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

